    <briefdescription>
<para>Registry for <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1FileIO" kindref="compound">FileIO</ref> implementations. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Provides a mechanism to register and load <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1FileIO" kindref="compound">FileIO</ref> implementations by name. This allows the REST catalog (and others) to resolve <ref refid="classiceberg_1_1FileIO" kindref="compound">FileIO</ref> implementations at runtime based on configuration properties like &quot;io-impl&quot;. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
